platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Miniclips 8 Ball Pool delivers a clean online billiards experience that awards players for speedy turns. We found ourselves collecting rare pool cues and training to clear tables faster, with higher scores and longer combos. An alluring level-up system and the ability to bet your in-game currency on the outcome of head-to-head matches makes jumping online for a quick game as rewarding as it is intense.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Finally, we can put that trigonometry to use!
